{"hash":"b4b17e22bff2fc2f31b44f38d499c1ec813b464635d0c7e923755ffad314be6c","display_name":"Seriki yakub","profile_url":"https://gravatar.com/qubuhubincs","avatar_url":"https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/b4b17e22bff2fc2f31b44f38d499c1ec813b464635d0c7e923755ffad314be6c","avatar_alt_text":"","location":"Ng","description":"Hey! I\u2019m Kubu \u2014 a visionary developer, blockchain innovator, and builder of smart AI systems. I specialize in creating intelligent, decentralized, and future-focused technology solutions that push boundaries.From full-scale blockchains to AI copilots and automation tools, my work is all about solving real problems with code. I'm passionate about building systems that are secure, scalable, and designed to empower users and developers alike.\ud83d\ude80 Projects by Kubu\ud83d\udd17 Fadaka Blockchain + Swift Beta Wallet My custom-built Layer 1 blockchain with smart contract support, peer-to-peer networking, and a vibrant token system.\ud83d\udd39 Swift Beta is the official wallet \u2014 featuring faucet access, token swaps, QR tools, and live transaction signing.\ud83d\udd39 Built with Go, Solidity, and a powerful HTML/CSS Jekyll interface.\ud83e\udd16 Project Pilot AI Your on-chain project assistant.\ud83d\udd39 Connects directly to GitHub, smart contracts, and local files\ud83d\udd39 Built with Python + FastAPI\ud83d\udd39 Supports code refactoring, GPT chat, and secure transaction broadcasting\ud83e\uddec Congen-AITrain AI on your own terms.\ud83d\udd39 Upload CSVs and build models instantly with a Streamlit UI\ud83d\udd39 Auto-generates docs and supports deployable web tools\ud83d\udd39 Built for creators, analysts, and learners\ud83d\udce6 Bizz Automation ToolkitAI meets business automation.\ud83d\udd39 Chat assistant, JWT-protected API, QR gen, and wallet connectivity\ud83d\udd39 Runs on FastAPI, integrated with the FDAK token\ud83d\udd10 Universal CertForgeA cross-platform certificate generation and signing system.\ud83d\udd39 Web + CLI tools for identity certs, APK/EXE signing, and TLS certs\ud83d\udd39 Admin dashboard, SMTP delivery, and revocation support\ud83e\udde0 AgbakoAIAn advanced AI system with modular agents for intelligent coordination, data analysis, and secured automation.\ud83d\udcbc What I Work With:Code: Go, Python, Solidity, JavaScriptFrameworks: FastAPI, Streamlit, Hardhat, JekyllTools: Docker, IPFS, GitHub Actions, Vercel, RailwayFields: Blockchain, AI, Web4, Automation, DevOps, Certificate Infrastructure\ud83d\udd25 Currently Cooking:The official Fadaka DEX with FX stable pairsA hosted version of Congen-AI for public model trainingUpgraded CertForge with mobile app integrationFollow my journey as Kubu \u2014 where code meets innovation, and every project is a step toward a smarter, more connected world","job_title":"CEO","company":"Qubuhub/fluukpe/auraecosystem","verified_accounts":[{"service_type":"github","service_label":"GitHub","service_icon":"https://gravatar.com/icons/github.svg","url":"https://github.com/Web4application","is_hidden":false},{"service_type":"linkedin","service_label":"LinkedIn","service_icon":"https://gravatar.com/icons/linkedin.svg","url":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/web4hub","is_hidden":false},{"service_type":"twitch","service_label":"Twitch","service_icon":"https://gravatar.com/icons/twitch.svg","url":"https://twitch.tv/kubulee","is_hidden":false},{"service_type":"twitter","service_label":"X","service_icon":"https://gravatar.com/icons/x.svg","url":"https://x.com/web4app","is_hidden":false}],"pronunciation":"","pronouns":"","header_image":"url('https://1.gravatar.com/userimage/268500768/76dd2be9fb9b1836eba9675f136f55b5?size=1024') no-repeat 50% 50% / 100%","hide_default_header_image":false,"background_color":"linear-gradient(138deg, rgba(15, 44, 133, 1) 0%, rgba(142, 48, 112) 55%, rgba(71, 34, 44, 1) 100%)","section_visibility":{"hidden_contact_info":false,"hidden_feeds":false,"hidden_links":false,"hidden_interests":false,"hidden_wallet":false,"hidden_photos"